label: uncl5375
comment: Code specifying the type of price.

values.label: Cancellation price
values.comment: Price authorized to be charged in the event of an order being cancelled.

values.label: Per ton
values.comment: To indicate that the price applies per ton.

values.label: Minimum order price
values.comment: A code to identify the price when the minimum number is purchased.

values.label: Export price
values.comment: A code to identify a price for the export market.

values.label: Range dependent price
values.comment: A code identifying the price for a specific range of purchase quantities.

values.label: Competitor price
values.comment: Price given by competitor.

values.label: Active ingredient
values.comment: The price is referring to the active ingredient.

values.label: As is quantity
values.comment: The price is referring to the measured quantity.

values.label: Catalogue
values.comment: Code specifying the catalogue price.

values.label: Contract
values.comment: Code specifying the contract price.

values.label: Consumer unit
values.comment: The price is referring to the consumer unit.

values.label: Distributor
values.comment: Code specifying the distributor price.

values.label: ECSC price
values.comment: Price registered at European Commission Steel and Carbon office (DG III).

values.label: Net weight
values.comment: Code specifying the net weight price.

values.label: Price catalogue
values.comment: Code specifying the catalogue price.

values.label: Per each
values.comment: Code specifying the price per item.

values.label: Per kilogram
values.comment: Code specifying the price per kilogram.

values.label: Per litre
values.comment: Code specifying the price per litre.

values.label: Per tonne
values.comment: Code specifying the price per tonne.

values.label: Specified unit
values.comment: Code specifying the price per specified unit.

values.label: Provisional price
values.comment: Code specifying a provisional price.

values.label: Gross weight
values.comment: Code specifying the gross weight price.

values.label: Quoted
values.comment: Code specifying the quoted price.

values.label: Suggested retail
values.comment: Code specifying the suggested retail price.

values.label: To be negotiated
values.comment: Code specifying that the price has to be negotiated.

values.label: Traded unit
values.comment: The price is referring to the traded unit.

values.label: Theoretical weight
values.comment: Weight calculated on ordered dimension (length, width, thickness) not on final dimension (e.g. steel products).

values.label: Wholesale
values.comment: Code specifying the wholesale price.

values.label: Gross volume
values.comment: The price is calculated based on gross volume.
